    <sys:String x:Key="RunningOldMineCraftUsingArm64JreWarning">
        Eh Gnot Ix Naiq Gnad Oad Ec Naij JRE Iew Nuj Uog Aij Ihs Gnix Nuy Arm64。
        Ed Neb Nab Oal Oaij Ihs Gnen Ek Ed Gnix Nuy Nin Uy Uoy Nad MineCraft Il Ihs，Iaz Af Uw Gnen Ek Ihs Gnix Nuy Ed Nah Oab Ous Il Ihs Naug Gnaix Arm64 Gnix Nuy Gnahc Gnehz Gnahs Gnot Ix。
        LauncherX Nef Ub Gnaij Ihs Gnahc Iuh Gnaij natives Gnod Iq Gnix Nij Uog Aij Gnot Ix Ed Gniy Iud Iew Nauh It，It New Ed Gnod Iq Uf Uix Iy Ek Gnen Ek Uoy Ehz。
        Oad Nauh Eiq Ihs Gnahc Gniq It New Naix Uhc Oug Ur X86 Ed Uog Aij JRE Gnod Iq Ic Iaz Ihs Gnahc Gnib Ihs Gnix Nuy。
    </sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="JreVersionTooHighWarning">
        Ed Ez Naux Naiq Gnad Nin Java Neb Nab [{0}] Neb Nab Ed Uiq Oay Ous Ix Uoy El Uy Oag [{1}]，
        Ed Neb Nab Nix Gnoy Ihs Java Gnen Gnix Ix Uoy Oag It Iy Ek Gnen Ek Nar Ius，Gnix Nuy Gnahc Gnehz Af Uw Ix Uoy Ihz Oad Iuh Gnen Ek Ey Nad。
        Gnix Nuy Gnahc Gnehz Af Uw Ix Uoy Oug Ur，Ed Uiq Oay Ous Ix Uoy Oad Nauh Eiq Ihs Gnahc Gniq Java Neb Nab。
    </sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="FailedToInitAuthenticator">Iab Ihs Iq Gnehz Nay Auh Ihs Uhc</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="FailedToInitAuthenticatorDetail">Iab Ihs Iq Gnehz Nay Auh Ihs Uhc，Gnix Oaix Uoy Ed Uh Gnahz Ahc Naij Gniq</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="CurrentLaunchSettings">Ihz Iep Gnod Iq Ed Naiq Gnad:</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LauncherRunningUnderTranslationWarning">
        Oad Ec Naij LauncherX Iaz Gnix Nuy Gnen Ek ARM64 Ed In Om Iq Il Uhc X86 Gnohz Gnij Nauh，Gnix Nuy Gnahs Gnec Iy Nauhz Iaz LauncherX Gnahc Iy Ed Iaw Ihz Oail Iy Gnehc Oaz Ij Iy Gnaix Gniy Oad Uohs Gnen Gnix Ihz Oad Iuh Gnen Ek。
        It New Ed Ihz Oad Gnen Ek Gnix Nuy Gnec Iy Nauhz Gnoy Ihs：
        - Ec Naij Eh Eib Ihs Ed Euq Gnehz Af Uw Java Iat Gnauhz Gnix Nuy Ed Ihs Gnix Nuy
        - Ij Gnaij Gnen Gnix Eh Nay It Ed Gnohz Nay
        - Gnahc Iy Naix Uhc Gnen Gnog Nef Ub
        Iaz Aix Nix Gnohz Gnib Uog Aij Gnot Ix Ed Nin Ner Euq Ic Iaz Gniq LauncherX。
    </sys:String>
